of TV presenting.

00:01:07.780 --> 00:01:11.080 align:middle line:84%
But all of my measure
of happiness and success

00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:16.570 align:middle line:84%
was on external things, so on
the job, on what I looked like,

00:01:16.570 --> 00:01:18.940 align:middle line:90%
the money, the boyfriends.

00:01:18.940 --> 00:01:21.340 align:middle line:84%
