unfulfilled.

00:01:21.340 --> 00:01:24.760 align:middle line:84%
I was unwell and unhappy
and spiraling downwards.

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:28.030 align:middle line:84%
I was dealing with an
eating disorder, depression,

00:01:28.030 --> 00:01:30.460 align:middle line:90%
and anxiety, and panic attacks.

00:01:30.460 --> 00:01:34.570 align:middle line:84%
