a whole host of health issues

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:47.980 align:middle line:84%
from chronic fatigue,
thyroid problems,

00:01:47.980 --> 00:01:50.770 align:middle line:84%
so many different little
things, hormone imbalances,

00:01:50.770 --> 00:01:55.025 align:middle line:84%
high levels of mercury, CBO,
candida, like everything.

00:01:55.025 --> 00:01:56.400 align:middle line:84%
>> A lot of
autoimmune condition.

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:56.710 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:01:56.710 --> 00:01:57.880 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:01:57.880 --> 00:01:59.380 align:middle line:84%
And not only that,
it was starting

00:01:59.380 --> 00:02:01.010 align:middle line:90%
to manifest in my skin.

00:02:01.010 --> 00:02:03.840 align:middle line:90%
