00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:06.790 align:middle line:90%
I had eczema all over my face.

00:02:06.790 --> 00:02:08.620 align:middle line:90%
And I had acne.

00:02:08.620 --> 00:02:11.830 align:middle line:84%
