beautiful moment right now.

00:35:51.530 --> 00:35:55.010 align:middle line:84%
So by practicing some
sort of meditation

00:35:55.010 --> 00:35:57.500 align:middle line:84%
strengthens that
presence muscle.

00:35:57.500 --> 00:35:59.310 align:middle line:84%
